original_title: Clutch: Fortune Tellers Make a Killing Nowadays
overview: One the road with Clutch. Ride along from city to city as one of the hardest working bands does what it does best. Hear from the band, crew, fans and other contemporaries along the way. Over 110 Minutes with the veterans of the trade.
tagline: Disc 2 of Clutch Live at the 9:30 Club
title: Clutch: Fortune Tellers Make a Killing Nowadays
